# Mini Shop API

A modern e-commerce backend built with Fastify, TypeScript, Supabase, and Zod.


## 🚀 Features

* Authentication with Supabase
* JWT Authorization
* Role-based access control (Admin / User)
* Product Management
* Order System
* Order Items
* Zod Validation
* Fastify Middleware
* Supabase PostgreSQL
* Soft Delete Products
* Pagination Support
* Environment Variables
* TypeScript Support


# 🛠️ Tech Stack

* Node.js
* Fastify
* TypeScript
* Supabase
* PostgreSQL
* Zod
* JWT


# 📁 Project Structure

```bash
src/
│
├── config/
├── middleware/
├── modules/
│   ├── auth/
│   ├── products/
│   ├── orders/
│
├── types/
├── utils/
└── server.ts
```

---

# ⚙️ Installation

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Reem99-sina/mini-shop-api
cd mini-shop-api
```

---

## Install Dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

